# A3 + A2: Dict(Json) in a recursive type — a closed record of Json values
# (here numbers, since number <: Json) is consistent with Dict(Json).
` { type-def: { Json: "number | string | bool | null | [Json] | Dict(Json)" } }
unit: {}

` { type: "Dict(Json)" }
data: { a: 1, b: 2, c: 3 }

result: data
